<h1>Apples are red</h1>
<p>Apples are a type of fruit that grow on apple trees.</p>

<h2 class="apple-text">Why apples are cool:</h2>
<ul>
  <li>They come in many colors, but red is the most famous.</li>
  <li>Apples are healthy and delicious.</li>
  <li>There are over 7,500 varieties of apples worldwide.</li>
</ul>

<p class="apple-text">Here's a fun apple fact: The science of apple growing is called pomology!</p>

